  1→//axhob_operation
  2→{rbtgo_director_create}
  3→
  4→The
  5→{rbtr_governor}
  6→creates a
  7→{rbtr_director}
  8→{giam_service_account}
  9→with build management permissions:
 10→
 11→//axhoq_precondition
 12→* Execute {rbtoe_check_rubric_repo_url} using {rbtr_governor} RBRA credentials
 13→
 14→//axhoq_precondition
 15→* Execute {rbtoe_check_devconnect} to verify {rbtgi_source_connection} authorization
 16→
 17→//axhop_parameter_from_type
 18→{rbtr_director}
 19→. *Validate Input Parameters*:
 20→.. {rbbc_require}
 21→`«INPUT_INSTANCE»` provided as first argument
 22→.. {rbbc_store}
 23→`«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»` as `rb-director-«INPUT_INSTANCE»`
 24→.. {rbbc_store}
 25→`«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` as `«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»@{rbrr_depot_project_id}.iam.gserviceaccount.com`
 26→
 27→//axhoq_precondition
 28→* {rbbc_require}
 29→`BURD_OUTPUT_DIR` environment variable set and directory exists
 30→
 31→//axhos_step
 32→. *Authenticate as
 33→{rbtr_governor}*:
 34→.. Execute
 35→{rbtoe_governor_authenticate}
 36→.. {rbbc_store}
 37→`«GOVERNOR_TOKEN»` for subsequent API calls
 38→
 39→//axhos_step
 40→. *Create
 41→{rbtr_director}
 42→Service Account*:
 43→.. {rbbc_call}
 44→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/create[iam.serviceAccounts.create] with:
 45→... accountId: `«DIRECTOR_ACCOUNT_NAME»`
 46→... displayName: `Recipe Bottle Director («INPUT_INSTANCE»)`
 47→... description: `Create/destroy container images for «INPUT_INSTANCE»`
 48→... project:
 49→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 50→.. {rbbc_require}
 51→HTTP 200 response
 52→.. {rbbc_poll}
 53→with 3-5 second intervals for up to 15 seconds for propagation
 54→
 55→//axhos_step
 56→. *Verify Service Account Creation*:
 57→.. {rbbc_call}
 58→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/get[iam.serviceAccounts.get] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»`
 59→.. {rbbc_require}
 60→service account accessible
 61→
 62→//axhos_step
 63→. *Preflight: Ensure Pristine Key State*:
 64→.. {rbbc_call}
 65→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts.keys/list[serviceAccounts.keys.list] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»`
 66→.. {rbbc_store}
 67→`«EXISTING_KEYS»` from response `.keys[]`
 68→.. {rbbc_require}
 69→no keys with `keyType: USER_MANAGED` exist
 70→.. {rbbc_fatal}
 71→if USER_MANAGED keys found: "Manual cleanup required via Console"
 72→
 73→//axhos_step
 74→. *Generate Service Account Key*:
 75→.. {rbbc_call}
 76→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts.keys/create[serviceAccounts.keys.create] for `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with:
 77→... privateKeyType: `TYPE_GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS_FILE`
 78→.. {rbbc_store}
 79→`«DIRECTOR_PRIVATE_KEY_DATA»` from response `.privateKeyData` field
 80→.. {rbtoe_rbra_generate}
 81→converts `«DIRECTOR_PRIVATE_KEY_DATA»` to `«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»`
 82→
 83→//axhos_step
 84→. *Get Depot Project Number*:
 85→.. {rbbc_call}
 86→link:https://cloud.google.com/resource-manager/reference/rest/v3/projects/get[projects.get] for
 87→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 88→.. {rbbc_store}
 89→`«PROJECT_NUMBER»` from `.projectNumber` field
 90→
 91→//axhos_step
 92→. *Grant Project-Level Permissions*:
 93→.. {rbbc_call}
 94→link:https://cloud.google.com/resource-manager/reference/rest/v3/projects/setIamPolicy[projects.setIamPolicy] for
 95→{rbrr_depot_project_id}
 96→.. Add `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with roles:
 97→... `roles/cloudbuild.builds.editor` (submit and manage builds)
 98→... `roles/viewer` (read project resources)
 99→.. Policy version: 3
100→.. {rbbc_require}
101→IAM policy update successful
102→
103→//axhos_step
104→. *Grant
105→{rbtr_mason}
106→Impersonation*:
107→.. NOTE:
108→{rbtr_director}
109→submits builds that execute as
110→{rbtr_mason}.
111→This requires `serviceAccountUser` permission on
112→{rbtr_mason}.
113→.. {rbbc_call}
114→link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/setIamPolicy[serviceAccounts.setIamPolicy] for
115→{rbtr_mason}
116→service account
117→.. Add `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with `roles/iam.serviceAccountUser`
118→.. {rbbc_require}
119→IAM binding successful
120→
121→//axhos_step
122→. *Grant
123→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
124→Access*:
125→.. NOTE:
126→{rbtr_director}
127→uploads build sources to
128→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
129→before triggering builds.
130→.. {rbbc_call}
131→link:https://cloud.google.com/storage/docs/json_api/v1/buckets/setIamPolicy[buckets.setIamPolicy] for
132→{rbtgi_build_bucket}
133→.. Add `«DIRECTOR_EMAIL»` with roles:
134→... `roles/storage.objectCreator` (upload sources)
135→... `roles/storage.objectViewer` (verify uploads)
136→.. {rbbc_require}
137→bucket IAM update successful
138→
139→//axhoo_output_of_type
140→{rbtgi_rbra_file}
141→. *Display Installation Instructions*:
142→.. {rbbc_show}
143→Director created successfully
144→.. {rbbc_show}
145→RBRA file location: `«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»`
146→.. {rbbc_show}
147→installation command:
148→... `cp "«DIRECTOR_RBRA_FILE»" "{rbrr_director_rbra_file}"`
149→.. {rbbc_warn}
150→if
151→{rbrr_director_rbra_file}
152→already exists
153→
154→//axhoc_completion
155→Successful execution creates director service account.
